leads.lead_text: Medium trees to 20 m tall; adult leaves sublustrous, light green; buds borne on pedicels 2–6 mm long; fruits obconical to funnel-shaped, 6–7 mm long, 4–6 mm diam.
Small trees or mallees to 12 m tall; adult leaves blue-grey to blue-green or subglaucous to glaucous; pedicels 0–3 mm long; fruits obconical to slightly cupular, 3–5 mm long, 3–5 mm diam
Adult leaves subglaucous to glaucous, 5–7 cm long, 4–6 cm wide; fruits 3–4(–5) mm long, 3–4 mm diam.
Adult leaves blue-green to blue-grey, 3–5 cm long, 2–4 cm wide; fruits 4–5 mm long 4–5 diam.
